article_title: Aetna, Humana, Blue Cross Snag Obamacare's Bargain Shoppers

article_metadata.description: Americans shopping on government-run exchanges for health insurance based on the price of premiums leaned toward plans from Aetna’s Coventry business, Humana (HUM) or the array of Blue Cross plans sold by Wellpoint (WLP), according to a new study out this week.
